   <br /> <span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="line-height:15.75pt"><strong>A joint message from Citron Hygiene and Terminix Global Holdings.</strong></span><br /> <br /> <span style="line-height:15.75pt">As a valued customer of Citron Hygiene, we would like to make you aware of an important change to your <strong>Pest Control Service. </strong><strong><span style="font-weight:normal">We are pleased to announce Terminix Global Holdings (“Terminix”) has agreed to acquire Citron Hygiene’s pest control business in Canada, the US and UK. </span></strong>Founded in 1927, Terminix is a global leader in pest control and is committed to providing you with quality pest control service for years to come. Citron Hygiene remains committed to washroom and facility hygiene services and this deal does not impact those business lines.</span><br /> <br /> <span style="line-height:15.75pt"><strong><span style="font-weight:normal">To ensure there are no disruptions to your pest service, Citron and Terminix have jointly agreed to work together over the next 45 to 60 days to plan and execute a seamless transition of your pest service to Terminix. </span><u>During this time, a Citron technician will continue to service your business, and you can continue to contact Citron for all pest service-related needs.</u></strong><strong><span style="font-weight:normal"> You will notice some small changes, such as your Pest Control services being invoiced separately from your other hygiene services.</span></strong>&nbsp; <strong><span style="font-weight:normal">We commit to providing you with further communication regarding the changes you can expect closer to the time of Terminix assuming your pest control service.</span></strong></span><br /> <br /> <span style="line-height:15.75pt">Terminix will honour all existing pest control customer service agreements, service terms, and commitments, and you will continue to receive the same great service you have come to expect.</span><br /> <br /> <span style="line-height:15.75pt">“Citron Hygiene is pleased with our deal with Terminix, an industry leader for pest control services. We know our customers with pest control services will be in great hands for all their pest control needs. This transaction allows Citron to focus solely on further strengthening our leading global market position in washroom and facility hygiene services” noted Peter Farrell, Citron’s CEO.</span><br /> <br /> <span style="line-height:15.75pt">“Terminix’s objective is to be the preferred pest management services company in the eyes of our customers, our teammates, and the communities we serve. The acquisition of such a great business and team will further strengthen our ability to realize our objective in Canada. We are very excited about demonstrating our ability to provide the highest quality of pest control services to our newest customers” commented Doug Hart, Terminix’s Vice-President, International.</span><br /> <br /> <span style="line-height:15.75pt">Citron Hygiene and Terminix are committed to ensuring a smooth transition. In the meantime, should you have any questions or concerns with upcoming changes please reach out to Citron's Customer Success team at 800.643.6922 or your Citron Account Representative.</span></span></span> 
